21:13.605 --> 21:16.972
"My love for you is like a river

21:17.909 --> 21:21.310
"Like a summer breeze
That makes my soul shiver

21:22.681 --> 21:25.878
"One look from you
Is more precious than gold

21:26.852 --> 21:29.753
"Let's go get some barbecue
And get busy"

