22:03.055 --> 22:04.750
That's cool, though, baby.

22:04.823 --> 22:07.792
I'm a poet,
and it's a lot more ink in this pen.

22:09.027 --> 22:11.222
I think you have a talent for poetry.

22:11.296 --> 22:13.764
